        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\ntitle\n&lt;size:16&gt;&lt;b&gt;UC-04: List a Product - Activity Diagram&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/size&gt;\nend title\n\n|Seller|\nstart\n\n:Navigate to Seller Dashboard and click &#39;Add New Listing&#39;;\n\n|System|\n:Display product listing form;\n\n|Seller|\n:Enter product details (title, category, sub-category, brand, model, condition, price, stock, description, specifications);\n\n:Upload product images (1 to 8, JPEG/PNG, max 5MB each);\n\n|System|\n:Validate all required fields and image constraints;\n\nif (All images valid?) then (no)\n  :Display inline error for invalid image(s);\n  :Seller re-uploads corrected images;\n  note right: Alternative Flow 2 (loop back)\n  --&gt; :Upload product images;\nelse (yes)\nendif\n\nif (Seller wants to save as Draft?) then (yes)\n  :Save listing as Draft (not submitted, visible only to Seller);\n  stop\nelse (no)\nendif\n\n|Seller|\n:Click &#39;Submit for Review&#39;;\n\n|System|\n:Save listing with status &#39;Pending Review&#39; and upload images to cloud storage;\n\n:Notify Admin via email and in-app notification;\n\n:Display success confirmation to Seller;\n\nstop\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="U2y3R0-jDhVh8ACwDD4h-2">
